(487, 1, '2023-02-10 12:09:53', '2023-02-10 12:09:53', '<b>What it is: </b>A waterproof brow putty that softly shapes and fills in brows for a natural, mistake-proof look that lasts.\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> Free of parabens. It is also cruelty-free.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> This breakthrough putty glides on creamy and sets to a buildable powder finish, minus the powder fallout, for an instantly fuller, more defined look that won’t smudge. The complementary shades mimic brows’ gradient tones for the most natural-looking depth and dimension.\r\n\r\n<b>Clinical Results:</b> In an independent consumer study of 72 subjects:\r\n- 100% said it instantly fills in sparse brows for a natural look\r\n- 100% said it adheres to brows and doesn’t cake or flake\r\n- 98% said it’s smudgeproof and doesn’t transfer or rub off', 'Brow Harmony Shape & Fill Duo', 'Isononyl Isononanoate, Mica, Nylon-12, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Dimethicone/Vinyl Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Boron Nitride, Lauroyl Lysine, Diisostearyl Malate, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Calcium Silicate, Caprylyl Glycol, Dimethicone, Phenoxyethanol, Triethoxycaprylylsilane, Hexylene Glycol, Potassium Sorbate, [+/- May Contain/Peut Contenir: Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891)].', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'brow-harmony-shape-fill-duo', '', '', '2023-02-10 12:10:28', '2023-02-10 12:10:28', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mypham/?post_type=product&#038;p=487', 0, 'product', '', 0),
