(489, 1, '2023-02-10 12:12:45', '2023-02-10 12:12:45', '<b>What it is: </b>An eco-conscious and cruelty-free false lash collection that features House of Lashes\' bestselling Iconic false lashes in Iconic, Iconic Lite, and Iconic Mini.\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> Free of parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, sulfates SLS &amp; SLES, triclocarban, triclosan, and contains less than one percent synthetic fragrance. It is also vegan, gluten-free, cruelty-free, and comes in recyclable packaging.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> The lash with a name that says it all: Iconic lashes will transform any look from natural- or soft-glam to all-out glam. Whether you want the original and full style, Iconic, the more natural version, Iconic Lite, or the pair customized for smaller eyes, Iconic Mini, there’s an Iconic lash for all looks and eye shapes.', 'House of Lashes Iconic False Eyelashes', 'Synthetic Fibers, Cotton Nylon Band.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'house-of-lashes-iconic-false-eyelashes', '', '', '2023-02-10 12:12:45', '2023-02-10 12:12:45', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mypham/?post_type=product&#038;p=489', 0, 'product', '', 0),
