(491, 1, '2023-02-10 12:14:40', '2023-02-10 12:14:40', '<b>What it is: </b>A weightless, liquid-to-powder eyeshadow that blends seamlessly for a quick, buildable wash of long-lasting, waterproof, crease-resistant color.\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> Free of parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, and sulfates SLS &amp; SLES. It is also cruelty-free.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> This quick and easy formula goes from liquid to powder in seconds. Velvety-smooth, creamy, and never sticky, it blends and builds easily before setting to a soft, satin finish that lasts all day—no creasing, smudging, fading, transferring, or drying out your skin.', 'Stay Vulnerable Liquid Eyeshadow', 'Isododecane, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Silica, Octyldodecanol, Hydrogenated Styrene/Isoprene Copolymer, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Mica, 1,2-Hexanediol, Caprylyl Glycol, Tocopheryl Acetate, Dicalcium Phosphate, Tin Oxide, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-di-t-butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Iron Oxides (CI 77491), Iron Oxides (CI 77492), Manganese Violet (CI 77742), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891).', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'stay-vulnerable-liquid-eyeshadow', '', '', '2023-02-10 12:15:16', '2023-02-10 12:15:16', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mypham/?post_type=product&#038;p=491', 0, 'product', '', 0),
