(495, 1, '2023-02-10 12:19:36', '2023-02-10 12:19:36', '<b>What it is: </b>A weightless, long-wearing, liquid lipstick with a soft-matte finish—born in a range of head-turning shades that look incredible on all skin tones.\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> Free of parabens. This product is also cruelty-free.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> Stunna Lip Paint delivers high-impact color with low-maintenance, long wear in a range of universal shades handpicked by Rihanna. With one stroke of its lip-defining precision wand, Stunna’s weightless, comfortable, soft-matte formula stays kissably smooth all day.', 'Stunna Lip Paint Longwear Fluid Lip Color', 'Isododecane, Dimethicone, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Hydrogenated Polycyclopentadiene, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Triethoxycaprylylsilane, Propylene Carbonate, Red 7 (Ci 15850), Yellow 5 Lake (Ci 19140), Yellow 6 Lake (Ci 15985).', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'stunna-lip-paint-longwear-fluid-lip-color', '', '', '2023-02-10 12:19:36', '2023-02-10 12:19:36', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mypham/?post_type=product&#038;p=495', 0, 'product', '', 0),
