(511, 1, '2023-02-10 12:39:29', '2023-02-10 12:39:29', '<b>What it is: </b>A super creamy, waterproof lip liner that glides on like a balm to define lips—in the same 10 rich, made-to-match shades as the Kind Words Matte Lipstick.<b>\r\n\r\nFormulation Type: </b>Lip Liner\r\n\r\n<b>Benefits: </b>Hydrating and Long-wearing\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> Free of parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, sulfates SLS &amp; SLES, triclocarban, and triclosan. It is also vegan, cruelty-free, and comes in recyclable packaging.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> Define and shape lips with one-swipe color and a soft matte finish. With an incredibly smooth, balm-like glide that won’t skip or tug, this waterproof liner not only stays put all day without smudging, but it keeps your lipstick in place, too. Keep the retractable tip sharp with the built-in sharpener.\r\n\r\n<b>Clinical Results:</b> In an independent consumer study of 51 people:\r\n- 100% said it draws smooth, even lines\r\n- 100% said lips don’t feel dry and that it’s comfortable to wear\r\n- 100% said it helps prevent lipstick from feathering or bleeding', 'Kind Words Lip Liner', 'Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Isohexadecane, Synthetic Wax, Mica, Isododecane, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Microcrystalline Wax/Cera Microcristallina/Cire microcristalline, Polybutene, Silica, C13-15 Alkane, VP/Hexadecene Copolymer, Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax/Copernicia Cerifera Cera/Cire de carnauba, Paraffin, Ethylene/Propylene Copolymer, Fragrance/Parfum, Caprylyl Glycol, Diisostearyl Malate, Gardenia Florida Fruit Extract, Glyceryl Caprylate, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Nelumbo Nucifera Flower Extract, Nymphaea Odorata Root Extract, Polyglyceryl-2 Diisostearate, Linalool. +/- (May Contain/Peut Contenir) Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850).', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'kind-words-lip-liner