(537, 1, '2023-02-10 13:07:49', '2023-02-10 13:07:49', '<b>What it is: </b>A dark spot corrector facial serum with four percent niacinamide and one percent ethyl vitamin C to visibly reduce dark spots and discoloration to improve skin clarity.\r\n\r\n<b>Skin Type:</b> Normal, Dry, Combination, and Oily\r\n\r\n<b>Skincare Concerns:</b> Dark Spots\r\n\r\n<b>Highlighted Ingredients:\r\n</b>- Niacinamide: Helps reduce the look of dark spots.\r\n- 1% Ethyl Vitamin C: Helps to visibly improve skin clarity.\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> This product is vegan.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> This dermatologist-tested treatment for dark spots on the face is formulated with four percent niacinamide and one percent ethyl vitamin C serums to visibly reduce age spots, melasma, and other discolorations for more even-looking skin. The gentle hyperpigmentation serum is suitable for all skin types, even sensitive.\r\n\r\n<b>Clinical Results:</b> In a 12-week consumer self-assessment:\r\n- 87% said skin tone looks more even\r\n- 81% said dark spots look minimized', 'Bye Bye Dark Spots 4% Niacinamide Serum', '-Niacinamide: Helps reduce the look of dark spots.\r\n-1% Ethyl Vitamin C: Helps to visibly improve skin clarity.\r\n\r\nAqua/Water/Eau, Propylene Glycol, Glycerin, Niacinamide, Peg/Ppg/Polybutylene Glycol-8/5/3 Glycerin, Hydroxypropyl Tetrahydropyrantriol, Caffeine, 3-O-Ethyl Ascorbic Acid, Citric Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Ppg-6-Decyltetradeceth-30, Salicylic Acid, Xanthan Gum, Sodium Citrate, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Potassium Hydroxide, Disodium Edta, Limonene, Geraniol, Citronellol, Tocopherol, Parfum/Fragrance.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'bye-bye-dark-spots-4-niacinamide-serum', '', '', '2023-02-10 13:07:50', '2023-02-10 13:07:50', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mypham/?post_type=product&#038;p=537', 0, 'product', '', 0),
