(539, 1, '2023-02-10 13:10:13', '2023-02-10 13:10:13', '<b>What it is: </b>A high-strength serum with 15 percent pure vitamin C to visibly improve skin’s brightness, firmness, stubborn discoloration, and dull and uneven tone.\r\n\r\n<b>Skin Type:</b> Normal, Dry, Combination, and Oily\r\n\r\n<b>Skincare Concerns:</b> Dark Spots, Fine Lines and Wrinkles, and Dullness\r\n\r\n<b>Formulation:</b> Liquid\r\n\r\n<b>Highlighted Ingredients:\r\n</b>- Vitamin C (L-Ascorbic Acid) 15%: Visibly improves firmness, fades dark spots, and brightens dull skin.\r\n- Ferulic Acid and Vitamin E: Enhance the benefits of vitamin C while protecting skin from environmental damage.\r\n- Hyaluronic Acid (Sodium Hyaluronate): Helps skin retain hydration while reducing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.\r\n\r\n<b>Ingredient Callouts:</b> Free of parabens, formaldehydes, formaldehyde-releasing agents, phthalates, mineral oil, retinyl palmitate, oxybenzone, coal tar, hydroquinone, sulfates SLS &amp; SLES, triclocarban, and triclosan. It is also cruelty-free and comes in recyclable packaging.\r\n\r\n<b>What Else You Need to Know:</b> Formulated at an ideal pH level of three and featuring 15 percent stabilized L-ascorbic acid, vitamin E, ferulic acid, hyaluronic acid, and a targeted peptide, this concentrated serum fades the look of sun damage and post-breakout marks while visibly addressing dullness and loss of firmness for a luminously healthy look.', 'C15 Vitamin C Super Booster', '-Vitamin C (L-Ascorbic Acid) 15%: Visibly improves firmness, fades dark spots, and brightens dull skin.\r\n-Ferulic Acid and Vitamin E: Enhance the benefits of vitamin C while protecting skin from environmental damage.\r\n-Hyaluronic Acid (Sodium Hyaluronate): Helps skin retain hydration while reducing the appearance of fine lines and wrinkles.\r\n\r\nWater (Aqua), Ascorbic Acid, Butylene Glycol, Ethoxydiglycol, Glycerin, PPG-26-Buteth-26, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Pentylene Glycol, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Sodium Hyaluronate, Hexanoyl Dipeptide-3 Norleucine Acetate, Lecithin, Ferulic Acid, Panthenol, Bisabolol, Oryza Sativa (Rice) Bran Extract, Propyl Gallate, Sodium Gluconate, Sodium Hydroxide, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin.', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'c15-vitamin-c-super-booster', '', '', '2023-02-10 13:10:14', '2023-02-10 13:10:14', '', 0, 'http://localhost/mypham/?post_type=product&#038;p=539', 0, 'product', '', 0),
